## <a id='major-features'></a>New Features in Ops Manager v2.2

## <a id='multi-dc'></a> Multiple Data Centers on vSphere

Ops Manager now allows you to configure multiple vSphere data centers to a single BOSH director. You can add additional data centers in the **vSphere Config** pane of your vSphere BOSH Director tile.

<p class="note"><strong>Note: </strong>If you are using the Ops Manager API and there are multiple vSphere configs, the <code>iaas_configuration</code> key is omitted from the response.</p>


